    Relationship

    public abstract class AbstractRelationship<A extends AppUser,B extends DataObject,L extends AbstractRelationship.Link<A,B>>
extends RelationshipLinkManager<A,B,L>
    abstract Link class that encodes an editable relationship between an AppUser and a domain object and used to implement RelationshipProvider and RoleSelector for the domain object. How roles are actually encoded into the link object is deferred to the sub-class.
